      "message": "dbwrapper: accept optional testing leveldb::Env in DBParams\n\nAdd a `testing_env` field to `DBParams` that, when non-null, is used as\nthe leveldb environment instead of the default or in-memory env. The\ncaller retains ownership. This allows test and fuzz harnesses to inject\na custom `leveldb::Env` for deterministic control.",
